{"tid":2169130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學者冀勿棄議會戰線","createTime":"2020-08-22T08:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T09:02:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a6c8dccacadaf13d3c761332f2c9aa15b7dd8c0","tid":2169130,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/FWDM4WIQNFET3KCZ3WGENHG6IA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FFWDM4WIQNFET3KCZ3WGENHG6IA%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6XlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=12983eca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FFWDM4WIQNFET3KCZ3WGENHG6IA%2F&h=3ba8d699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/FWDM4WIQNFET3KCZ3WGENHG6IA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n學者冀勿棄議會戰線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_ZpJgmsIKuwxD8iXb84DcjbmC1E=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NCY54JBB5NAOXCND2ML4RWQMSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_ZpJgmsIKuwxD8iXb84DcjbmC1E%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNCY54JBB5NAOXCND2ML4RWQMSY.jpg&h=153e5fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】城大公共政策學系教授葉健民（圖）昨在報章撰文指，除非港人全面放棄議會戰線，否則若民主派以總辭離開議會，便會將「公民社會幾十年努力近一筆勾銷」，更把港人的投票權一同奪走，令港人喪失「絕無僅有」的政治參與權。<br />\n<br />\n葉健民指，若民主派總辭放棄議會戰線、放棄議員擁有的權力，「便差不多等於把公民社會幾十年艱苦經營努力建設的社區網絡、與政策社群的深厚聯繫，以至和各個公共政策持份者的對話空間也一筆勾銷」，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰籲多角度考量<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。，因此「不會有任何國家政府、政客因為民主派延任一年，或者全面杯葛而轉變對香港以及中國的態度」。他指，在考慮民主派去留問題上「不應建基於『原則性』的原因」，反而應從多角度如人民授權、議會獨裁、發聲空間、憲制權力等因素去考量。"},{"pid":"b1f51b3be93a9e4097263c4672e8da2a5239e8c7","tid":2169130,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"就算冇延遲<br />\n<br />\n都dq左咁多人<br />\n<br />\n想問點議會抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b6ebec1d3185d00a8a37977ccded38b04ad88e","tid":2169130,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"做乜呢幾日咁多呢d 人 <br />\n<br />\n叫人支持泛民參加人大委任嘅議會"},{"pid":"06701de2a327879e4f7f41ff80dfea80f970afcd","tid":2169130,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,&quot;總辭派&quot;只會要求泛民總辭,&quot;本土派&quot;,&quot;熱狗派&quot;會取而代之入議會,之後投共之說會唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}